paxE800Desc: PAX’s E800 is a visually striking game-changer. Elegance is everything in-store, yet cash registers have never made for a stylish checkout experience until today. The E-series runs on PAXBiz® powered by Android™, giving you access to a whole world of third-party business apps and solutions.
